OL,3,CPoverty hidden behind some of the UK's
OL,4,Cmost picturesque locations, says report
OL,6,FA new report has suggested that rural
OL,7,Fpoverty is often 'hidden' behind some
OL,8,Fof the most beautiful parts of the
OL,9,Fcountry like Cornwall, resulting in
OL,10,Fthe government 'overlooking' the
OL,11,Fdeprivation facing people living there.
OL,13,FThe research, carried out by the
OL,14,FDiocese of Truro and Plymouth Marjon
OL,15,FUniversity, claims that the
OL,16,Fdeprivation being overlooked by the
OL,17,Fgovernment is then leading to poor
OL,18,Fservice provision and inappropriate
OL,19,Fpolicy making.
