OL,3,CPoverty hidden behind some of the UK's
OL,4,Cmost picturesque locations, says report
OL,6,FResearchers have coined the term
OL,7,F'pretty poverty' to help illustrate
OL,8,Ftheir argument that the government's
OL,9,Fmethod of measuring deprivation fails
OL,10,Fto take into account the challenges
OL,11,Ffaced by people living in rural
OL,12,Flocations like Cornwall.
OL,14,FResearchers say the Index of Multiple
OL,15,FDeprivation (IMD), used by the
OL,16,Fgovernment, does not put enough
OL,17,Femphasis on issues like poor transport
OL,18,Flinks faced by many people in those
OL,19,Fareas.
