OL,3,CPoverty hidden behind some of the UK's
OL,4,Cmost picturesque locations, says report
OL,6,FProfessor Tanya Ovenden-Hope explains
OL,7,Fwhy he thinks the Index of Multiple
OL,8,FDeprivation can 'hide' the depth of
OL,9,Fpoverty in areas like Cornwall
OL,11,FThe government says the IMD is a valid
OL,12,Fand trustworthy way to measure poverty
OL,13,Fbut is working to investigate
OL,14,Fdeprivation in rural areas and will
OL,15,Frelease a report on the issue next
OL,16,Fmonth.
