OL,3,CPoverty hidden behind some of the UK's
OL,4,Cmost picturesque locations, says report
OL,6,FCornwall was ranked 83 out of 317
OL,7,Flocal authority areas for overall
OL,8,Fdeprivation in 2019's IMD. The top six
OL,9,Fmost deprived neighbourhoods in
OL,10,FCornwall according to the IMD are all
OL,11,Fpredominantly urban.
OL,13,FBut, report authors say, there is a
OL,14,Fkey difference between urban and rural
OL,15,Flife and those should be taken into
OL,16,Faccount when the deprivation is being
OL,17,Fmeasured.
