OL,6,F"The problem with that is, if there is
OL,7,Fa low density population as there is
OL,8,Fin Cornwall, you have many affluent
OL,9,Fpeople, you also many people in
OL,10,Fextreme poverty - you have an average-
OL,11,Fing effect.
OL,13,F"We need smaller units of measurements
OL,14,Fso that those places have the reality
OL,15,Fof those places recognised by
OL,16,Fgovernment. If we are to get the
OL,17,Fcorrect resources to our rural areas,
OL,18,Fthey need to understand what is
OL,19,Fhappening."
