OL,3,CPoverty hidden behind some of the UK's
OL,4,Cmost picturesque locations, says report
OL,6,FThe report explores the idea that
OL,7,Frural issues are frequently hidden
OL,8,Fbehind a facade of beauty, tourism and
OL,9,Fcommunity spirit that show those in
OL,10,Fthe countryside and seaside locations
OL,11,Fare 'living with prosperity.'
OL,13,FThe authors believe the tools used to
OL,14,Fgive public investment and support are
OL,15,Fnot built to capture the complexity of
OL,16,Frural deprivation.
OL,18,FWhat are the key findings of the
OL,19,Freport?
