OL,4,Cmost picturesque locations, says report
OL,6,FThe study said seasonal work, a lack
OL,7,Fof public transport and strong
OL,8,Fcommunity resilience can all be
OL,9,Ffactors which lead to a
OL,10,Fmisunderstanding of levels of
OL,11,Fdeprivation.
OL,13,FThe report will be shared with local
OL,14,Fand national policy makers.
OL,16,FA Ministry of Housing, Communities and
OL,17,FLocal Government spokesperson said:
OL,18,F"The Indices of Deprivation meet the
OL,19,Fhigh standards of trustworthiness,
OL,20,Fquality and value required for
OL,21,Fstatistics.
